{"tid":424085,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"兩日多5班機取消  香港快運CEO孭鑊辭職","createTime":"2017-10-04T11:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T02:37:56.000Z","uid":133959,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8733929e68c0d43128ab46471705f68cca12bf38","tid":424085,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"18:15<br />\n香港快運航空，10.1黃金周期間突然有18班往返香港至韓國仁川、日本名古屋、關西的航班，引起政府及旅客關注，其後運輸及房局要求快運需提交報告解釋事件，香港快運行政總裁安浩恩周日（1日）向乘客就事件致歉，又承諾本月8日後的航班不會再取消。<br />\n<br />\n言猶在耳，今日和昨日（3-4日）快運又有5班航班取消，令10.1期間至少23班航取消；影響最少2,000名乘客。<br />\n<br />\n香港快運發言人回應指，上次因航空訓練員「集體劈炮」導致候命機組人員不足事件，周日已經交待，之後沒有因此事而導致其他航班取消，但並沒有進一步解釋這兩天取消5班航班的原因。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171004/57290316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171004%2F57290316&d=frl0UrnvNjjxBuJ1bdA3sgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=b37049a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171004%2F57290316&h=a43cccfe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171004/57290316</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n19:24<br />\n在十一黃金周假期突然取消18班航班的香港快運，外電報道指，行政總裁安浩恩（Andrew Cowen）已經引咎辭職。報道指，其離職與連日來航班取消及公司訓練人手不足有關，另外亦有兩名公司高層同時離任。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道指安浩恩已離職，並獲兩名知情人士證實消息。消息指，安浩恩離職跟航班取消，以及公司訓練人手不足有關。安浩恩接受路透社與《南華早報》查詢時，都拒絕證實消息。<br />\n<br />\n香港快運上周五爆出取消航班後，安浩恩周日會見傳媒回應及致歉，當時承諾本月8日後不會再取消航班。<br />\n<br />\n在航運界打滾20多年的安浩恩，於2013年加入香港快運，兩年後升任行政總裁，任內推出多項廉價機票優惠搶客。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171004/57291299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171004%2F57291299&d=frl0UrnvNjjxBuJ1bdA3sgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=51a130dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171004%2F57291299&h=a1044f78\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171004/57291299</a>"},{"pid":"1c2a17b84dc5929f9f483c487ab5a0d5bc7b0877","tid":424085,"uid":133959,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:46:28.000Z","msg":"祭番張10月驚喜圖出黎先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/194606_3b6c22c6ee991f794bab866cf29b4826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F194606_3b6c22c6ee991f794bab866cf29b4826.jpg&h=4d7933ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfa164601fc2e94d731477de9bd0792a9ca84bf9","tid":424085,"uid":26467,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祭番張10月驚喜圖出黎先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/194606_3b6c22c6ee991f794bab866cf29b4826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F194606_3b6c22c6ee991f794bab866cf29b4826.jpg&h=4d7933ba&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得出做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5ee7679c0a825697141e2f8e4a5cbf64b26377","tid":424085,"uid":72186,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>祭番張10月驚喜圖出黎先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/194606_3b6c22c6ee991f794bab866cf29b4826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F194606_3b6c22c6ee991f794bab866cf29b4826.jpg&h=4d7933ba&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得出做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係夠晒驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a5911a7eb020b9909d21e6ce15ed420e5b46c6","tid":424085,"uid":58841,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"如果快運直接收皮就正啦<br />\n少左好多大種乞衣去污染日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\